A DIY HTML and CSS3 animation library
=========

Idoanimate is a set of javascript, css, html that can create animation based on HTML(5), not Flash at all. I'm going to pack it as a complete library to use it multiple times in my own projects, and may be yours.

  - Create animation objects based on div with background image and some animation CSS style
  - Written with my limited knowledges about Javascript OOP
  - Need much much more improvment

Version
-

0.0.3

Tech
-----------

Create animation objects based on div with background image and some animation CSS style

Installation
--------------

1. Clone the repo
2. Include idoanimate.js in your document
3. See my example. I'll provide a short guide soon.


